Class PayMedia

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.luis.kioskComponents.ePayment.PayResult
      • de.luis.kioskComponents.ePayment.PayMedia

  • public class PayMedia
extends PayResult
    Project: LUIS ePayment

    During a payment/refund transaction, this class is filled with the information about the payment media used. It contains all the details about the transaction and the card used.
